HEADWORD: Old Dominion
<hw>Old Dominion</hw>. <def>Virginia; -- a name of uncertain origin,
perh. from the old designation of the colony as ⟦ldquo⟧the Colony and
Dominion of Virginia.⟦rdquo⟧</def>⟦br⟧
